管仲纪念馆
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">外文名</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
Guan Zhong Memorial Hall
</dd>
</dl><dl class="basicInfo-block basicInfo-right">
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">地    点</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
淄博市临淄区齐陵街道办事处
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">建筑面积</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
3000平方米
</dd>
<dt class="basicInfo-item name">总投资达</dt>
<dd class="basicInfo-item value">
2000万元
</dd>
</dl></div>
